    "heroSubtitle": "We believe game publishing should be fair, transparent, and open. Magnetite is the platform where developers own their games and earn what they deserve.",
    "missionKicker": "// OUR MISSION",
    "missionHeading": "Scaling Rust games from game-jam to AAA",
    "missionP1": "Magnetite is building the full stack for Rust games — hosting, matchmaking, real-time netcode, payments, and analytics — so developers only write game logic. A tiny single-file arcade game and a 64-player multiplayer title use the same SDK.",
